Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.88,0:00:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我胸中的鼓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.92,0:00:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你延續而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.88,0:00:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.92,0:00:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使受了傷也無妨  不轉移目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.92,0:00:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想熱切、激烈地生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.92,0:00:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我永不放棄的堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.92,0:00:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想緊緊抱著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.92,0:00:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去或痛楚都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.92,0:01:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引導至鮮明的、一瞬間的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.92,0:01:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我胸中的鼓勵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.92,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你延續而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.63,0:01:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.83,0:01:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續留在這艘艦裡會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.83,0:01:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾‧拉巴伯‧溫拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.77,0:01:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是鋼彈駕駛員中最錯誤的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十八話\N[朝混沌出擊]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準不好啊，我在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去，有一個時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以一個按鈕\N決定所有戰鬥的勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種討厭的精神的根源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種叫MD的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而它們的代表就是那艘天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果從戰爭裡\N失去[人]這特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝利和敗北也是悲慘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.19,0:03:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神不會向任何一方伸出祂的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說漂亮話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你，戰火擴散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.24,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手應該只有我就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做好心理準備了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然，但我今次不會留手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以來多次反抗死的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今次我也要反抗它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.49,0:04:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你們有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.66,0:04:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先帶我們去萬年和平號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去萬年和平號?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.63,0:04:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去傑克斯就會如願以償
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要進入萬年和平號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.61,0:04:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變天秤座的軌道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯的意圖…難道…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.22,0:04:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，他的目標是終結地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何要阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣，我們的贖罪就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,計算出衝入大氣層的地點了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據現在的情況推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座能衝入地球大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞落北半球大陸的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是69%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時釋放出來的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推測大約有6千兆噸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣，米利亞爾特司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坎斯，萬年和平號和天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若這兩艘戰艦\N撞落那個蔚藍的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季節就會停頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫長的冬天就會來臨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在萬年和平號的推進系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.07,0:05:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壞掉的前提下計算出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.24,0:05:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬年和平號是我過去的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它會理解我的意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.68,0:05:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈們真的會讓你做嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.75,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.29,0:05:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們當然會擋在我面前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在等他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和歷史的必然推展或大義不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是名為戰鬥專家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯‧馬吉斯也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等! 希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為何一定要出擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座會毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有任何戰鬥的理由了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特和白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯…並不認為輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，傑克斯和特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.78,0:06:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來也無意結束這場戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說如果你出戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭就會結束嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會打倒傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著是特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣，戰爭就會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，如果妳活下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平就會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我唯一能為妳做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾答應妳 我會保護妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護妳和這個地球圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有戰鬥一途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.56,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行! 不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，你打算去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.68,0:07:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛…我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這房間…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD的控制室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有裝了零式系統的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和零式系統有直接聯系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰鬥意思驅使所有MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾‧溫拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我決鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在零式系統之間的戰鬥裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.89,0:09:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，今次會有何結果呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.32,0:09:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為能憑自己的意思戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話，我不想戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果不那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就不會投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭也不會結束  對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，零式系統和血肉之驅的意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來分出哪一方優勝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拒絕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳為何執著於戰爭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不惜這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁慈的卡特爾小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為何戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了親人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不令大家傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只好戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.97,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的爸爸為了\N不令我傷心而戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要美麗地戰鬥後而死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，妳也憎恨戰爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.79,0:10:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!破壞和殺戮\N並非戰爭的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.33,0:10:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要打倒的敵人\N在我們心裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.83,0:10:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信凌駕戰爭的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信渴望和平的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你說你一直為了大家在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.57,0:10:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但大家有為你做過甚麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.61,0:10:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我戰鬥並非為了要別人報答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，你是小朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再打…桃樂絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星出賣了鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星的居民殺了你的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，武裝起來的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼也不理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就向地球宣佈要獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.08,0:11:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直以來的戰鬥\N全是白費啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關懷別人的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過份關懷的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種最壞的事態啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體上船了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.63,0:11:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，就此飛向MO-II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.24,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再呼喚會妨礙他們戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但希洛打算去死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，我求你，請答話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命不值錢，特別是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等我，卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.09,0:12:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦，對不起\N我有俗務要辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.86,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別介意，夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見，不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣，迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去到萬年和平號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.21,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我們其中之一就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有人被拋開\N你也別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒那種時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有想穿越這種地方的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.11,0:13:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不該找到他們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神和瘟神要過去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚…甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我們的力量不能令宇宙統一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但地球卻逐漸統一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那位小姐的力量嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們 在和卡特爾少爺見面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不準死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不出真功夫嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是，你不能嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我不會留手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.63,0:14:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種純真 那種幼智 那種仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會令你們戰敗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只懂以這方式戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，因為這樣不停戰敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.98,0:15:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星的人\N才不用被捲入戰火之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就毫無改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為衛星的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正挑起戰爭就行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像米利亞爾特大人那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃樂絲，妳錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.83,0:15:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，應該讓全人類看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令他們不想再看見戰爭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.50,0:15:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲慘戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是這場戰爭的意義嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了令戰爭\N從人類的歷史裡消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.71,0:15:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒收武器不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不令人類的心改革…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不那樣做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.49,0:15:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類…就會像父親大人那樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我更仁慈呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那樣說，我也不會高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.73,0:16:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁慈是活下去的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡了力才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就最適合人類啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.27,0:16:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃樂絲…妳和從前的我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太憎恨戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.28,0:16:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能信賴自己的仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.12,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不可否定仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.62,0:16:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給特洛瓦教懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.56,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們非接受一切不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.13,0:16:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類需要那種仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類就沒有存在意義啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.11,0:16:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單純只是活下去的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.38,0:16:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…不會關懷任何人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.75,0:16:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連動物也不如的…種族啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.96,0:17:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼?為何不用那條龍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.47,0:17:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你堂堂正正決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猶疑嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.07,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當時為何不殺我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.34,0:17:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能殺死\N寥寥可數理解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要猶疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.50,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個只懂那樣蔑視別人的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥時始終只懂胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多少人\N為了你而死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.98,0:17:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,截至昨日合共99，822人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂，今日戰死的有多少人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在確定了的有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.62,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙82人，我軍105人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會把名字告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了戰鬥而犧牲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.04,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全都記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾邊塔、賽普提姆、班迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.64,0:18:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德利安、華卡、奧圖、本度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是不能忘懷的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.42,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對死者只能表示哀悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.09,0:18:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我希望你也明白這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.53,0:18:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們絕對不是白死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.74,0:18:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起…五飛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯? 你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五飛…我永遠的好友啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和你們戰鬥令我覺得自豪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.79,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這種結果…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會承認啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.83,0:19:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米利亞爾特…我先行一步了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.91,0:19:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.31,0:19:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次贏了…\N今次就不和我再戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特校，請下命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.59,0:19:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們世界國家軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.33,0:19:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在宣佈戰敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.07,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特…特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種羞恥的宣言不要我重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點通報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.11,0:20:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真偉大，特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.98,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳在那裡嗎? 桃樂絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才，地球方面\N發出戰敗宣言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰敗宣言?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.09,0:20:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，索敵隊說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯‧克修里那達已經戰死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那種事…不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.17,0:20:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.31,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會中止把這艘艦撞落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.07,0:20:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是米利亞爾特司令的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始最後噴射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.08,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家自己決定是否撤離吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝大家平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來出了問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某意思上或許是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣，真正的和平不會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.10,0:20:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不懂哭的女人真可悲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.74,0:21:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球方面認輸了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，只是那樣不會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.44,0:21:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙打算把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座和萬年和平號撞落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還應該能阻止那種事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.32,0:21:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒試過不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.49,0:21:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個能把不可能\N變成可能的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.73,0:21:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，沒辦法把這件事告訴他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去希洛那裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.40,0:21:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，推進能量用盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.84,0:21:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.31,0:21:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛 希洛
